author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-West International receives additional order from ABSA Bank
text:
Oct 19 West International Publ Ab :
* Received additional order from ABSA bank
* Delivery is scheduled in Q4 2015
* Order value is up to 1.3 million Swedish crowns ($158,000) Source text for Eikon:
Further company coverage: ($1 = 8.2305 Swedish crowns) (Gdynia Newsroom)
